    {
      "id": "stage-03",
      "order": 3,
      "title": "Práctica guiada",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Pr&aacute;ctica guiada &mdash; Comparaci&oacute;n y orden</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Pr&aacute;ctica guiada</h1>\n  <p><span class=\"badge\">5.&ordm; grado</span><span class=\"badge\">Ejercicios</span></p>\n\n  <h2>Parte A: Comparar</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 1 &mdash; Escribe $&gt;$, $&lt;$ o $=$</h4>\n    <p>Coloca el signo correcto entre cada par de n&uacute;meros:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $4\\,800\\,000$ ___ $5\\,200\\,000$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $12\\,345\\,678$ ___ $12\\,345\\,687$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $999\\,999$ ___ $1\\,000\\,000$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">d) $50\\,300\\,100$ ___ $50\\,300\\,100$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">e) $78\\,650\\,000$ ___ $78\\,605\\,000$</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 2 &mdash; Verdadero o falso</h4>\n    <p>Indica si cada comparaci&oacute;n es verdadera (V) o falsa (F):</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $6\\,000\\,000 &gt; 5\\,999\\,999$ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $230\\,500 &lt; 203\\,500$ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $15\\,000\\,000 &gt; 14\\,999\\,999$ ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Parte B: Ordenar</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 3 &mdash; Ordena de mayor a menor</h4>\n    <p>$3\\,250\\,000$ &mdash; $890\\,000$ &mdash; $3\\,205\\,000$ &mdash; $12\\,400\\,000$ &mdash; $3\\,250\\,001$</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 4 &mdash; Ordena de menor a mayor</h4>\n    <p>$45\\,000\\,100$ &mdash; $4\\,500\\,010$ &mdash; $45\\,001\\,000$ &mdash; $450\\,010$ &mdash; $45\\,000\\,010$</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Parte C: Problemas</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 5</h4>\n    <p>La poblaci&oacute;n de tres ciudades es:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Ciudad A: $2\\,350\\,000$ habitantes</li>\n      <li>Ciudad B: $2\\,530\\,000$ habitantes</li>\n      <li>Ciudad C: $2\\,305\\,000$ habitantes</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>a) &iquest;Qu&eacute; ciudad tiene m&aacute;s habitantes?</p>\n    <p>b) Ordena las ciudades de menor a mayor poblaci&oacute;n.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 6</h4>\n    <p>Escribe un n&uacute;mero que cumpla:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) Mayor que $5\\,000\\,000$ y menor que $5\\,100\\,000$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) Mayor que $99\\,999\\,999$ y menor que $100\\,000\\,001$</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"note\">\n    <strong>Respuestas:</strong><br/>\n    1a) &lt; &middot; 1b) &lt; &middot; 1c) &lt; &middot; 1d) = &middot; 1e) &gt;<br/>\n    2a) V &middot; 2b) F &middot; 2c) V<br/>\n    3) 12&thinsp;400&thinsp;000 &gt; 3&thinsp;250&thinsp;001 &gt; 3&thinsp;250&thinsp;000 &gt; 3&thinsp;205&thinsp;000 &gt; 890&thinsp;000<br/>\n    4) 450&thinsp;010 &lt; 4&thinsp;500&thinsp;010 &lt; 45&thinsp;000&thinsp;010 &lt; 45&thinsp;000&thinsp;100 &lt; 45&thinsp;001&thinsp;000<br/>\n    5a) Ciudad B &middot; 5b) C &lt; A &lt; B<br/>\n    6a) Cualquier n&uacute;mero entre 5&thinsp;000&thinsp;001 y 5&thinsp;099&thinsp;999 &middot; 6b) 100&thinsp;000&thinsp;000\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n      delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n    });\n  });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
